play-scala-crud is simple CRUD application. Project is intended to learn 
basics of play framework using Scala language.

To run:
	1> pull repo
	2> change directory to play-scala-crud
	3> ./activator run
	4> open http://127.0.0.1:9000/ in browser
	5> click on 'Apply this script now!'

explore the code. it's simple and useful to grasp the structure of play framework.
HAVE FUN!
